

[tile]

  simplest tile is 16x16 cells

  [features]

    [create tile] 

      when selecting cells, there should be an option to "create tile".
      when a tile is created, the square of the area selected should be 
      saved and should appear in the "tile gutter

      we should also be able to hit a "tile" button in our list of buttons.
      that should pop up with a 16x16 cell area with a certain kind of boarder

    [delete tile]

    [save tile]

    [animate tile]

      a tile can be animated
      an animated tile is just a list of tiles that play
        on a loop over the cells that are associated with that tile. 
        The cells that the tile is "over".
      if we make an animated tile, we should be able to select multiple 
        regular tiles, and order it in a "selected tile gutter"

    [tile gutter]

      there is a tile gutter on the right side of the screen 


    [selected tile gutter]

      
      
